To thoroughly test the functionality of the Movie Trivia Quiz program, follow these steps:

Run the program by executing the Python script file (movie_trivia_quiz.py) in your terminal or command prompt.
When prompted, choose a difficulty level for the quiz by entering a number between 1 and 3.
The program will display a series of trivia questions based on the selected difficulty level.
For each question, enter your answer in the terminal and press Enter.
If you answer a question incorrectly, the program will provide a hint to help you.
After answering all the questions, the program will display your final score.
Decide whether to play again or exit the program.
If you choose to play again, repeat steps 2-7 with a different difficulty level.
By following these steps, you can thoroughly test the functionality of the Movie Trivia Quiz program and ensure it operates as expected.
